/*
 * Error Test: E4008 - main declared with a return type (empty body)
 *
 * Regression for #1482: used to fire both E4008 ("main cannot have a
 * return type") and a contradictory cascade E3024 ("main must return
 * a value"). Typechecker now rewrites main's effective return type to
 * void after E4008 so all downstream return checks see it that way.
 */

do main() -> string {
}
